1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:03,281
The Seller registers a represented receivable.

2
00:00:03,281 --> 00:00:07,903
Compliance and Risk then issue separate, scoped attestations.

3
00:00:07,903 --> 00:00:11,829
The Seller derives certificates and creates one private

4
00:00:11,829 --> 00:00:14,283
request for each invited Funder.

5
00:00:14,283 --> 00:00:18,132
These are real Daml contracts, with role-specific signatories

6
00:00:18,132 --> 00:00:21,981
and observers, while the raw debtor identity remains

7
00:00:21,981 --> 00:00:23,424
with the Seller.
